title.value: Cross-version Extension `R5.ServiceRequest.orderDetail` for use in FHIR R4

description.value: This cross-version extension represents the FHIR R5 element `ServiceRequest.orderDetail` for use in FHIR R4.

purpose.value:
This extension is part of the cross-version definitions generated to enable use of the element `ServiceRequest.orderDetail` as defined in FHIR R5 in FHIR R4.
The source element is defined as: `ServiceRequest.orderDetail` 0..* `BackboneElement`
Across FHIR versions, the element set has been mapped as: * R5: `ServiceRequest.orderDetail` 0..* `BackboneElement` * R4B: `ServiceRequest.orderDetail` 0..* `CodeableConcept` * R4: `ServiceRequest.orderDetail` 0..* `CodeableConcept`
Following are the generation technical comments: Element `ServiceRequest.orderDetail` is mapped to FHIR R4 element `ServiceRequest.orderDetail`.
